msgstr ""

#: ../../../mastering/virtualenv.rst:96
msgid ""
"Use the generator ``virtualbuildenv`` to activate an environment that will "
"set the environment variables for Autotools and Visual Studio."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../mastering/virtualenv.rst:99
