msgid ""
"In the previous example of the ``cmake_installer`` recipe, even if the "
"cmake_installer package doesn't declare the ``self.env_info.path`` variable, "
"using the virtualrunenv generator, the ``bin`` folder of the package will be "
"available in the PATH. So after activating the virtual environment we could "
"just run ``cmake`` and we will be executing the cmake of the package."
